title: All.The.Small.Things.S01E02[DVBRip.XVID]DsG
description: Layla encourages Michael to be more ruthless in his pursuit of success, so he announces that everyone must audition to keep their places in the choir. When church caretaker Shrek finds himself thrown out, Esther - still reeling from the news that her husband has moved in with his new woman - encourages her old friend to ask for another chance. Drama, starring Sarah Alexander, Neil Pearson, Sarah Lancashire and Clive Rowe.
